 2017-11712017-09-22,  ,  DFO,  , 
ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Ontario Fishery Regulations, 2007
PrecisRegulations Amending the ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 2007 in order to apply the differential daily catch and retain limit for non-residents currently in place in the Border Waters Area for sauger, wallleye, and lake trout throughout Fiisheries Management Zone 5 (i.e. sauger and walleye daily limit of 2; lake trout daily limit of 1).
